<section class="py-20 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
        Sound Familiar?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
        These problems cost businesses thousands in lost revenue every month
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20 p-8 rounded-xl border border-red-200 dark:border-red-800">
        <div class="text-4xl mb-4">⏰</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">
          Slow Response Times
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
          Losing leads because you can't respond to social media inquiries fast enough. Every minute costs you potential customers.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-orange-50 dark:bg-orange-900/20 p-8 rounded-xl border border-orange-200 dark:border-orange-800">
        <div class="text-4xl mb-4">📊</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">
          Manual Data Entry Hell
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
          Wasting hours every day copying information from emails and messages into spreadsheets. It's tedious and error-prone.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-yellow-50 dark:bg-yellow-900/20 p-8 rounded-xl border border-yellow-200 dark:border-yellow-800">
        <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🔄</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">
          Missed Follow-ups
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
          Disorganized customer tracking means you forget to follow up. Leads go cold and opportunities slip through the cracks.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
